"what if everything you knew about Hobbits was wrong meet Flores man a tiny human species that thrived on Indonesia's Flores Island just over 50,000 years ago bones first discovered in 2003 shocked archaeologists worldwide these Hobbits stood only about a meter tall therefore their existence challenged our perceptions of human evolution as scientists delved deeper questions arose were these Hobbits a separate species or mere dwarfed humans recent DNA studies bring us closer to the truth but their sudden disappearance remains a mystery fueling debates today thus while Hobbits may not dwell in Middle Earth real life counterparts once trod the Lush jungles of Indonesia "